snippet.title: Soni Soni | Ishq Vishk Rebound | Rohit Saraf, Pashmina| @DarshanRavalDZ@jonitamusic, Rochak,Gurpreet
snippet.description:
"Soni Soni" is the ultimate anthem for dance lovers blending irresistible beats with heartfelt lyrics. Perfectly crafted for Gen Z, this track promises to get you moving and feeling the love. Get ready to vibe and groove to your new favorite hit! from the much-awaited movie "Ishq Vishk Rebound." Starring the charming Rohit Saraf and the beautiful Pashmina Roshan, and the mesmerizing voices of Darshan Raval, Jonita Gandhi & Rochak Kohli, this track is set to steal hearts. Lyrics Penned By Gurpreet Saini With music by the talented Rochak Kohli, this track promises a perfect blend of love and melody. Don't miss it!

Stay updated with the latest videos from Tips Official, Subscribe on the below link.
http://youtube.com/tipsofficial

In Theatres From 21st June 2024

Song Details :
Song Name: Soni Soni 
Singers: Darshan Raval, Jonita Gandhi & Rochak Kohli
Music Director: Rochak Kohli
Music Producer: Sharan Rawat
Lyricist: Gurpreet Saini
Choreographer : Vijay Ganguly
Director of Photography (Song): Debojeet Ray

Movie Details : 
Producers- Ramesh Taurani and Jaya Taurani
Director- Nipun Avinash Dharmadhikari
Lead Cast- Rohit Saraf, Pashmina Roshan, Jibraan Khan, Naila Grrewal
Secondary Cast- Kusha Kapila, Supriya Pilgaonkar, Akarsh Khurana, Shilpa Vishal Shetty, Shataf Figar, Anita Kulkarni and Sheeba Chadda 
Story and Screenplay writers- Dr. Vinay Chhawal, Vaishali Kamalakar Naik, and Ketan Pedgaonkar
Additional Screenplay writers- Akarsh Khurana and Nipun Avinash Dharmadhikari
Dialogue writer- Akarsh Khurana & Lisha Bajaj
Director of Photography- Milind Jog
Audiography & Sound Design- Anirban Sengupta
Music- Rochak Kohli 
Lyrics- Gurpreet Saini, Kumaar and Gautam G Sharma
Choreographer- Vijay Ganguly
Editor- Chandan Arora
Production Designer- Nikhil Kovale
Costume Designers- Abhilasha Devnani & Manisha Melwani

Music On Tips Music (Tips Industries Ltd.)

Lyrics: 
Dil Mera Dil Mera 
Ki Karan
Meri Baat Maane Na

Kitna Tenu Chahe 
Tenu Aaye 
Meri Yaad Na

Kehna Tenu Kehna
Ik Tu Hi 
Bas Pyaar Hai Mera

Koi Nahi Tere Pehle 
Koi Hona
Tere Baad Na

Akhiyaan Le Jaayein Meri Jaan 
O Soni Soni
Mujhko Bachaye Teri Haan

Gall Meri Manja 
Tu Meri Banja
Ke Mitthi Mitthi Neendraan Da Khwaab Hai Tu

Hai Mera Kya Kasoor
Tu Dendi Ae Sukoon 
Jo Utre Na Aisi Woh Sharaab Hai Tu

O Soni Soni
Tu Meri Banja

O Soni Soni
Tu Meri Banja

O Mere Sohneya Chandni Raaton Mein
Main Toh Aagayi Phir Teri Baaton Mein

Kaisi Tu Mere Naal Chaal Chaleya Ve
Dil Tere Naal Naal Chaleya Ve
Asar Ae Poora Saal Chaleya Ve
O Sohneya Ve

Akhiyaan Le Jaayein Meri Jaan 
O Soni Soni
Mujhko Bachaye Teri Haan

Gall Meri Manja 
Tu Mera Banja
Ke Mitthi Mitthi Neendraan Da Khwaab Hai Tu

Hai Mera Kya Kasoor
Tu Dinda Ae Sukoon 
Jo Utre Na Aisi Woh Sharaab Hai Tu

Tu Meri Banja
Ke Mitthi Mitthi Neendraan Da Khwaab Hai Tu

Hai Mera Kya Kasoor

O Soni Soni
Tu Meri Banja

snippet.title: Thank you 6 Million Friends | Chef Alandra's Chocolate Cake Recipe in Tamil
snippet.description:
Our Madras Samayal family has now grown to 60 lakh subscribers and we are now a family of 6 million friends. I thank you for you all for your love and support over all these years. Your positive feedback and encouraging comments have enabled me to continue this journey. I am so proud to be part of this family and thank you for providing me this opportunity to share the love of cooking with you.
#chocolatecake #cakerecipeintamil 

 To celebrate this special occasion chef Alandra will be making an ultra moist chocolate cake recipe. Please do try this cake recipe at home and share it with your friends and family. This chocolate cake is perfect for all celebratory occasions. Also, please do share your feedback about the recipe in the comments below. All the best and happy cooking!



Ingredients:
For the ultra moist Chocolate cake recipe:
3 Eggs
1/2 cup Milk (125 ml)
1/2 cup Curd (125 ml)
1/2 cup Oil (125 ml)
1/4 cup melted Butter (25g)
2-3 tsp Vanilla extract
1.5 cup Sugar (300g)
1.5 cup Maida (185g)
1/2 cup Cocoa powder (50g)
1.5 tsp Baking powder
3/4 tsp Baking Soda
1/4 tsp Salt
Bake at 175C /350 F for 35-38 min (8*8 inch square pan)

For the Chocolate frosting:

1/2 cup cream 
1 cup semi sweet chocolate chips (150g)
2 tbsp Butter
50g powdered Sugar (can increase up to 75 g to suit our preference)
If using  dark chocolate increase the amount of powdered Sugar
If using  Milk Chocolate only 2 tbsp of powdered Sugar would be sufficient.

snippet.title: Shiddat Episode 33 Teaser - Har Pal Geo
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Shiddat Episode 33 Teaser - 21st May 2024 - Har Pal Geo

Asra, a beautiful and cherished young woman, has led a life filled with love and care from her family. In contrast, Sultan, a determined and charismatic perfectionist, overcomes the challenges of his troubled childhood to consistently achieve his desires.

Despite their stark personality differences, Asra falls in love with Sultan. However, after they marry, Asra realizes that Sultan is not the ideal man she had envisioned. To please him, she sacrifices her desires and undergoes a significant transformation.

This revelation becomes the catalyst for an unending series of problems between them. The journey through marital life becomes a complex maze as Asra and Sultan attempt to navigate challenges, each trying to mold the other according to their own will and preference.

Will Asra and Sultan change for each other, or will the growing list of problems between them persist? When Asra discovers the reality about Sultan, how will she react? Is Sultan contemplating leaving Asra? Can love overcome all obstacles, or are some differences too profound to bridge?

snippet.title: Prashant Kishor's Bold Prediction For 2024 Lok Sabha Elections
snippet.description:
#prashantkishor #loksabhaelections2024 #pmmodi #ndaalliance #indialliance 
Join Business Today's Executive Director Rahul Kanwal in an exclusive conversation with renowned political analyst Prashant Kishor as they delve into the 2024 Lok Sabha poll predictions. Prashant Kishor forecasts that the BJP is poised to secure around 300 seats in the upcoming elections. Kishor dismisses the possibility of the BJP winning 370 seats, as recently claimed by Prime Minister Narendra Modi, calling it motivational rhetoric rather than a realistic goal. He emphasizes that while surpassing 370 seats is improbable, the BJP is also unlikely to drop below 270 seats. According to Kishor, the BJP's performance in the 2024 elections is expected to be on par with the previous Lok Sabha results, potentially achieving around 303 seats or slightly more. Tune in to this insightful discussion to gain a deeper understanding of the political landscape as the nation approaches the crucial 2024 elections. 400 paar? BJP out? Or struggle for 272? As election fever peaks, political strategist Prashant Kishor shares his insights on the current state of play. Kishor talks of the vulnerabilities that have built up over 10 years of the Modi government, what to expect from Modi 3.0, and why he thinks there will be many more street protests over the next five years than in the past decade. Kishor‚Äôs also betting his reputation and future on being able to win the Bihar assembly elections in 2025.
-----------------------
Thank You for watching! Do not forget to Like | Comment | Share 
-----------------------

snippet.description:
Hey Guys 
This Video shows different scenarios of Girls in Parallel Universe . How the world will be if there is role reversal girls behaved like boys and boys acted like girls , universe would be so different . Scenes like wife going on job and husband packing lunch for her , girls acting like guys and eve teasing boys on street , shadi rishta and dowry , politicians during elections making policies for boys , brave sisters rescuing their brothers , world where period leave and pregnancy leave persists , girl things and struggles becomes boy things and boy struggles . Sister after college catching brother at cafe marrying him off and not letting him continue his studies , so many more fun and relatable points  , you will love it and Relate with this video.. Enjoy and laugh out loud. 

This video is filled with  memories and situations we all have been in . 
Relish and Relive those fun moments

Episode 4091: Gokuldham Ho Gaya Hai Divide
--------------------------------------------------------
Sodhi gets angry at Chana Kumar and Kurmura Kumar. Iyer drops all the lemons on the road, and Tapu Sena feels bad for not helping Jethalal. Later, Kurmura Kumar's man scolds the Gokuldham members for assisting Iyer when lemon juice gets into his eyes.

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.description:
Hai tera, hai mera, humara ye saara jahaan! 
Presenting the second song from ‚ÄòMr. and Mrs. Mahi‚Äô, ‚ÄòAgar Ho Tum‚Äô is composed by Tanishk Bagchi. Penned by Kausar Munir and sung by Jubin Nautiyal, the magical song features Rajkummar Rao and Janhvi Kapoor in it.

#AgarHoTum #RajkummarRao #JanhviKapoor #MrandMrsMahi 

Composer - Tanishk Bagchi 
Singer - Jubin Nautiyal

Written by Nikhil Mehrotra & Sharan Sharma

Main khud ko bhula doon,

Agar ho tum toh

Chaand main tere haath mein rakh doonga!

Song : Nakhro 
Singer : Ndee Kundu
Female Lead : Malika Kaliraman

Lyrics / Composer : Ankurr

Je Galti Te Madam Ji Bannjo Hamare
Ram Ki Syu Gabru Ne Aajenge Nazaare 

Tere Laare Mai Bhi Yo Pyaar Tove Nakhro

Ek Teri Haan.... Na Hove Nakhro
Ek Teri Haan.... Na Hove Nakhro
Ek Teri Haan.... Na Hove Nakhro

Gabru Ne Haaye Tera Moh Itna
Jnu Aave Se Kisaan Ne Zameen Ka
Chaar Mein Te 3 Din Kattjawange 
Haseen Scene Bna Gel Coffee Peen Ka
Zulf Aankhya Te Jadd Dekhe Tu Htaake
Aaja Se Swaad Fer Jeen Ka
Gali Ke Me Tere Chora Maare Jaawe Gede
Kaam Hoya Pda Mera Yo Routine Ka 

Teri Rakh Sirhaane Photo Chora Sove Nakhroo

Ik Teri Haan.... Na Hove Nakhro
Ik Teri Haan.... Na Hove Nakhro

Ar Saanj Ne Tu Chadde Se Sharaab Si
Baawla Sa Hoya Tere Paache Sisaraala

Barainnn Hotthan Te Konya Chup Todti

Chore Ne Ishaare Pe Tu Krawe Salsa
Haan Krke Khatam Kr Baat Si
